&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;Across 31 global offices, we draw on the full depth of the firm so clients can&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;operate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;with clarity, act with confidence, and lead with trust. This collaborative approach has established FGS as a market leader: we are consistently ranked Band 1 for Crisis &amp;amp; Risk Management and Litigation Support by Chambers and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;Partners, and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;were ranked the #1 Global M&amp;amp;A PR firm by deal value and deal count for four consecutive years (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;Mergermarket&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;, 2025).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
